page_title: Quickstart - getting started with Azure OpenAI assistants (preview) in AI Studio
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI assistants with new features like code interpreter in AI Studio (Preview).
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure AI hub resource with a model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.- An Azure AI project in Azure AI Studio.
